description:
In this edition of Magnus CarlsTrend, Jack and Miles discuss the hot goss on Adam Levine, Hurricane Fiona making landfall in Puerto Rico, "Messy" Magnus Carlsen's rematch resignation, the Queen's funeral, South Carolina's Title IX recognition ceremony being ruined by Shane Beamer, and Adnan Syed getting relesased from prison!
